reviewText: Bought these for my wife for Christmas. They are the Waltons. What more can you say? At least I don't have to pay the cable company $50 a month to see reruns of 30-year-old shows.
Title: The Waltons: The Complete Seasons 1-9

reviewText: This is a good tv show about a family who lived through the great depression and later world war ll. I didn't like this show when I was little but tastes change. Its a good show about a family who lived through the bad times and the good times. Mostly bad. You should get this.
Title: The Waltons: The Complete Seasons 1-9

reviewText: It teaches good morals, it a wholesome series the whole family can watch and and since it took place in the the 1930s through the 1960s it does not become dated.  I recommendf it to all.

reviewText: I LOVE The Walton's series!  I wish we still had these wonderful, wholesome shows on tv now.  Even though I watched it as a child, I SO get the lessons now.  And, the history lessons.
